LOOLA Top in Yellow Tribal
description: Perfect to throw on with a pair of leggings, shorts, or a pair of Loola swimming briefs. With a comfortable elastic neckline and loose fitting sleeves, it's easy to slip on and head out for the day.

description: It's comfortable, light weight, and perfect for all seasons.  With its midi-length and feminine flutter sleeve, its darling as is or layered up for Fall. For an edgier look, pair with a utility jacket, denim vest, or scarf. Your little chica will be looking too cool for preschool.

name: Loola "Baby Step" Pant in Grape
description: The "Baby Step" lounge pant; a hybrid of harem and legging, for the babies + Mamas who want to keep it comfortable while still remaining fashion forward. With it's looser fit, they're perfect for your little to throw on before hopping on a plane, tagging along on a late date-night, heading to a Mommy+Me yoga class, or simply hanging around the house. Baby loungewear never looked so good.
